        "title": "Ecology and evolution of viruses infecting uncultivated SUP05 bacteria as revealed by single-cell- and meta- genomics", 
        "published": "2014-08-29T00:00:00Z", 
        "versionDate": "2014-08-29T00:00:00Z", 
        "volume": 3, 
